BugReports: https://github.com/jansteinfeld/jmleIRT/issues
Description: Implements joint maximum likelihood estimation (JMLE) for item parameters in the Rasch model (1PL). Provides methods for bias correction of item parameter estimates and weighted likelihood estimation (WLE) of person parameters.
